# hope-11-shape-divider

### 示例
![image](data:image/png;base64,)

### 引入
```vue
import ShapeDivider from '@/uni_modules/hope-11-shape-divider/components/hope-11-shape-divider/hope-11-shape-divider.vue'
```

### 使用
```vue
<ShapeDivider>
  <image :src="image4" mode="aspectFill" class="image"></image>
</ShapeDivider>
```

### 属性
参数|类型|默认值|说明
---|:--|:--|:---
shape|String|waves|形状，可选值：waves, waves-opacity, curve, curve-asymmetrical, triangle, <br>triangle-asymmetrical, tilt, arrow, split, book
color|String|#ffffff|颜色
width|Number, String|100|宽度，单位为 %
height|Number, String|100|高度，单位为 rpx
flip|String|false|翻转，即水平翻转，支持形状：waves, waves-opacity, curve-asymmetrical, <br>triangle-asymmetrical, tilt
invert|Boolean|false|倒转，即垂直翻转，支持形状：waves, curve, curve-asymmetrical, triangle, <br>triangle-asymmetrical, arrow, split, book
position|Boolean|top|位置，可选值：top, bottom
